data.text:
Daniel Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Daniel is recorded 946,747 times globally, ranking it as the 13th most common name worldwide.

Daniel is most prevalent in United States of America, with 124,598 occurrences, making it the 11th most popular name in the country.
